text: Sheikh Humaid bin Rashid Al Nuaimi III (; born 1931) is the ruler of the emirate of Ajman and a member of the UAE Supreme Council of the Union. He is the 10th ruler of Ajman. He became rule when his father Sheikh Rashid bin Humaid Al Nuaimi III died on September 6, 1981. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Emirati people Category:Current national leaders
